 ief Vibe Officer Kristina growing up in a traveling circus in the Soviet U
 nion. After years of traveling through Europe and California\, we’ve fin
 ally found "home" right here in the Triangle area. Tucked beside the Works
 pace Provision Co. building\, Grub Smokehouse is our way of bringing peopl
 e together through approachable\, world-class flavor. What to expect at Gr
 ub: Made from Scratch: We start every morning fresh\, slow-smoki
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
